headline: PayPal (PYPL) Partners with Spark to Inject $1B PYUSD Liquidity
summary: PayPal Holdings, Inc. (NASDAQ:PYPL) is one of the most undervalued financial stocks to buy according to Wall Street analysts. On September 25, PayPal partnered with decentralized finance platform Spark to expand on-chain liquidity, aiming to grow PYUSD deposits from $100 million to $1 billion. headline: Walmart-Backed OnePay to Add Bitcoin and Ether Trading to Finance App: CNBC
summary: The service will be powered by Zerohash, and will put OnePay in line with competitors like Venmo, Cash App, and PayPal.

headline: PayPal (PYPL): Exploring Valuation Following New Google Partnership and AI-Powered Shopping Expansion
summary: PayPal Holdings (PYPL) is making headlines following its new multiyear partnership with Google. Under this agreement, PayPal will serve as the primary payments processor across Google platforms. The collaboration also involves building AI-powered shopping agents designed to redefine e-commerce experiences. See our latest analysis for PayPal Holdings.
